    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>1 tea bag or 1 teaspoon loose tea leaves</li>
            <li>1 cup boiling water</li>
            <li>Milk (optional)</li>
            <li>Sugar or sweetener, to taste</li>
            <li>Lemon or mint for garnish (optional)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Tags</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Tea</li>
            <li>Beverage</li>
            <li>Hot Drink</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Place the tea bag or tea leaves in a teapot or mug.</li>
            <li>Pour boiling water over the tea bag or leaves.</li>
            <li>Let it steep for 3-5 minutes, or longer for a stronger flavor.</li>
            <li>If desired, add milk to the tea and stir.</li>
            <li>Sweeten the tea with sugar or your preferred sweetener, adjusting to taste.</li>
            <li>Optional: Garnish with a slice of lemon or a sprig of mint.</li>
            <li>Stir and enjoy your soothing cup of Tea!</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

